    <mj-section padding="0px">
      <mj-column  background-color="#eff0f0">
        <mj-text padding-left="40px" padding-top="0" padding-bottom="5px" font-family="Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif" font-size="14px" line-height="150%">
        <h3>Here’s how it works:</h3>
        <ul>
        <li>
        	Carriers have an opportunity to enter the sweepstakes daily 
        </li>
        <li>
        There will be 5 winners drawn per day between 10/24/2021 and 10/30/2021 
        </li>
        <li>
        	To be entered for the daily drawing carriers must <strong>complete at least one load</strong> that was booked using <strong>Relay Load Board’s Post A Truck,</strong> or enter without completing a trip by following the steps outlined below
        </li>
        <li>
        	5 winners of a <strong>$400 Amazon.com gift card</strong> will be drawn daily – one winner per carrier
        </li>
        <li>
        	If your company is one of the 5 daily winners, you'll be notified as a winner through the primary administrators email* registered in Amazon Relay 

        </li>
        </ul>
        <p style="font-size: 9pt">*Please review or update your company’s Relay account information before the promotion period begins</p>
        </mj-text>
          <mj-button font-family="Helvetica" background-color="#ff9900" color="black">
          <strong><a href="https://www.amazon.com/ap/signin?openid.pape.max_auth_age=86400&openid.return_to=https%3A%2F%2Frelay.amazon.com%2Floadboard%2Forders&openid.identity=http%3A%2F%2Fspecs.openid.net%2Fauth%2F2.0%2Fidentifier_select&openid.assoc_handle=amzn_relay_desktop_us&openid.mode=checkid_setup&openid.claimed_id=http%3A%2F%2Fspecs.openid.net%2Fauth%2F2.0%2Fidentifier_select&pageId=amzn_relay_desktop_us&openid.ns=http%3A%2F%2Fspecs.openid.net%2Fauth%2F2.0">POST YOUR TRUCK</a></strong>
         </mj-button>
          <mj-text>
          <p align = center>
          NO PURCHASE OR PAYMENT NECESSARY TO ENTER OR WIN.  Open to legal residents of 50 United States and D.C. who are at least age 18 and a primary administrator of an authorized motorized carrier signed up and accepted into the Amazon Relay program (via www.relay.amazon.com) at the time of entry. Must have completed a trip 30 days before the Sweepstakes Period. “Sweepstakes Period” for each daily sweepstakes is from 12:00:01am through 11:59:59pm PT on each day from 10/24/21 to 10/30/21. To enter: during the Sweepstakes Period, either: (1) complete a trip using Amazon Relay Post A Truck feature; or (2) send an email to relaycommunication@amazon.com with subject line “Amazon Relay No Tricks, Just Treats Sweepstakes” with your name, address, USDOT Number, e-mail address associated with your relay.amazon.com account, and phone number in email body. For each daily sweepstakes (7 total), 5 winners will be selected at random to each win one $400 Amazon.com e-gift card. Odds of winning depend on number of eligible entries. Sweepstakes subject to Official Rules. Details and restrictions apply, so visit <a href="https://d3gefe8pnkczmm.cloudfront.net/AmazonRelayTruck-or-TreatSweepstakesOfficialRules.pdf">Relay</a> for Official Rules. Sponsor: Amazon Logistics, Inc., 410 Terry Avenue North, Seattle, WA 98109.  
          </p>
        </mj-text>
          
